<template>
    <form>
        <v-card class="px-10 py-10">
            <v-select
                v-model="select"
                :items="items"
                label="Property"
                required
                @change="$v.select.$touch()"
                @blur="$v.select.$touch()"
            ></v-select>
            <v-row>
                <v-col
                    cols="6"
                    sm="12"
                    md="6"
                    lg="6"
                >
                    <v-select
                        v-model="select"
                        :items="items"
                        label="Block/Wing"
                        required
                        @change="$v.select.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.select.$touch()"
                    ></v-select>
                </v-col>
                <v-col
                    cols="6"
                    sm="12"
                    md="6"
                    lg="6"
                >
                    <v-select
                        v-model="select"
                        :items="items"
                        label="Floor"
                        required
                        @change="$v.select.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.select.$touch()"
                    ></v-select>
                </v-col>
            </v-row>
        </v-card>
        <v-row>
            <v-col
                cols="12"
                sm="12"
                md="6"
                lg="6"
            >
                <v-card 
                    class="px-10 py-10"
                >
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="name"
                        :error-messages="nameErrors"
                        label="Name *"
                        required
                        @input="$v.name.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.name.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="name"
                        :error-messages="nameErrors"
                        label="Area(in Sq. ft)"
                        required
                        @input="$v.name.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.name.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                    <v-select
                        v-model="select"
                        :items="items"
                        :error-messages="selectErrors"
                        label="Type of the unit"
                        required
                        @change="$v.select.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.select.$touch()"
                    ></v-select>
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="name"
                        :error-messages="nameErrors"
                        label="Bedrooms"
                        required
                        @input="$v.name.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.name.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="name"
                        :error-messages="nameErrors"
                        label="Bathrooms"
                        required
                        @input="$v.name.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.name.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="name"
                        :error-messages="nameErrors"
                        label="Kitchens"
                        required
                        @input="$v.name.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.name.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                </v-card>
            </v-col>
            <v-col
                cols="12"
                sm="12"
                md="6"
                lg="6"
            >
                <v-card 
                    class="px-10 py-10"
                >
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="name"
                        :error-messages="nameErrors"
                        label="Status *"
                        required
                        @input="$v.name.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.name.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="name"
                        :error-messages="nameErrors"
                        label="Amenities"
                        required
                        @input="$v.name.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.name.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                </v-card>
            </v-col>
        </v-row>
        <v-row 
            class="mt-3"
        >
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>
                <v-btn
                    class="mr-4"
                    min-width="150"
                >
                    Clear
                </v-btn>
                <v-btn
                    color="primary"
                    class="mr-4"
                    min-width="150"
                >
                    Preview
                </v-btn>
        </v-row>
    </form>
</template>
<script>
export default {
    name : 'Unit'
}
</script>
